            "text": "<p>This collection was designed to reflect the all-encompassing, rich and deep love of God. A love that restores, pursues, and gently reminds us that we are seen and chosen. Each piece is designed to draw you into the deep well of his presence: steady, renewing, and full of grace.</p><p>Including 2 ESV Journaling Bibles, 3 NLT notetaking Bibles, 2 Women's CSB Study Bibles, and 4 notebooks, this collection is an invitation to rest, to be restored, and to remember that you are deeply loved by a God who meets you in your weariness, brings light into darkness, and faithfully leads your heart back to peace.</p>",
